Class PlusLoopbackState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.v4.runtime.atn.ATNState
      • org.antlr.v4.runtime.atn.DecisionState
        • org.antlr.v4.runtime.atn.PlusLoopbackState
  • public final class PlusLoopbackState
extends DecisionState
    Decision state for A+ and (A|B)+. It has two transitions: one to the loop back to start of the block and one to exit.
